msgid ""
"--- WHAT YOU HAVE LEARNED ---\n"
"  Chapter 1: Getting Started with NVDA\n"
"  Chapter 2: Your Keyboard\n"
"  Chapter 3: Reading Text\n"
"  Chapter 4: Browse Mode and Web Navigation\n"
